hobn gedint in, in di poylishe armey

00:24:23.260 --> 00:24:24.384
un

00:24:25.183 --> 00:24:27.134
iz zey geven frayntlekh, yo.

00:24:27.985 --> 00:24:31.115
hot im, in nayn un draysikstn yor hobn zey

00:24:31.115 --> 00:24:33.915
mir hobn zey nisht bavizn tsu mobilizirn

00:24:34.313 --> 00:24:36.800
vorn di milkhome iz gegangen azoy shnel

00:24:36.800 --> 00:24:41.610
az in meshekh fun tsvey vokhn hobn di daytshn farnumen gants Poyln.

00:24:43.257 --> 00:24:45.110
ven es gedoyert nokh a

00:24:45.110 --> 00:24:48.785
a vokh tsvey dray, volt men mir ge- oykh genumen in di armey.

00:24:48.859 --> 00:24:50.810
f- ikh bin geshtanen oyf a komisye

00:24:51.120 --> 00:24:54.742
un ikh bin geven gut far di armey. ikh bin geven gezunt, yo.

00:24:57.297 --> 00:24:59.366
hot ir gehat poylishe fraynt?

00:24:59.271 --> 00:25:03.112
yo. kh'hob gehat poylishe fraynt, yo. kh'hob gehat.

00:25:03.658 --> 00:25:06.099
hob mit zey gearbet tsunezamen, yo.

00:25:06.983 --> 00:25:09.829
mayn shvoger hot gearbet UNK tsunezamen.

00:25:07.033 --> 00:25:08.225
ho-

00:25:09.683 --> 00:25:10.925
hobn zey a mol

00:25:09.970 --> 00:25:11.274
efsher, efsher

00:25:11.274 --> 00:25:15.025
efsher in harts hobn zey gefilt antisemitish

00:25:15.133 --> 00:25:16.679
ober der

00:25:16.770 --> 00:25:19.661
der balebos iz geven a yid, farshteyt ⟨ir vi se⟩

00:25:19.661 --> 00:25:22.535
hobn zey nisht gekont azoy aroysvayzn

00:25:22.609 --> 00:25:25.601
hot ir a mol gehert a shlekht vort akegn yidn

00:25:25.601 --> 00:25:27.429
fun, fun di fraynt ayere?

00:25:27.351 --> 00:25:28.745
NO, NO

00:25:29.545 --> 00:25:30.807
ye, zog ikh aykh

00:25:32.312 --> 00:25:36.592
andere flegn a mol, a mol makhn a vits, makhn a

00:25:36.592 --> 00:25:39.332
a JOKE gegn yidn, ober

00:25:40.902 --> 00:25:43.343
di, di merheyt iz gevezn

00:25:44.175 --> 00:25:45.688
in yene tsaytn

00:25:45.728 --> 00:25:48.641
nor fun di milkhome iz opgeredt ⟨derfun⟩

00:25:48.934 --> 00:25:51.594
ober hob ikh geleyent in, in di tsaytung

00:25:51.853 --> 00:25:53.993
az in Yerusholaim

00:25:53.993 --> 00:25:55.796
i- i- in YAD HASHEM

00:25:56.275 --> 00:25:58.716
iz do a por hundert polyakn

00:26:00.055 --> 00:26:01.956
vos zey hobn geratevet yidn

00:26:04.155 --> 00:26:05.347
un

00:26:06.265 --> 00:26:09.229
a teyl fun di polyakn lebn nokh

00:26:10.129 --> 00:26:12.840
vos di yidn in Amerike un Kanade

00:26:13.639 --> 00:26:15.067
forn tsu zey

00:26:15.546 --> 00:26:17.953
u- un shikn zey peklekh

00:26:19.140 --> 00:26:22.048
ober me kon dertseyln oyf di finger.

00:26:22.048 --> 00:26:23.128
s'iz geven

00:26:23.128 --> 00:26:26.424
⟨BUT⟩ di dray un a halb milyonen yidn hobn gelebt

00:26:26.464 --> 00:26:30.626
bloyz in Varshe hot gelebt efsher a fir hundert toyznt yidn.

00:26:31.223 --> 00:26:34.949
ir hot gezogt az ir hot gehat etlekhe kroyvim, etlekhe feters

00:26:34.665 --> 00:26:35.435
yo

00:26:34.949 --> 00:26:36.667
in Gritse.

00:26:36.505 --> 00:26:37.312
yo.

00:26:37.312 --> 00:26:38.417
nor ober

00:26:38.417 --> 00:26:42.000
ikh gedenk zey ven ikh bin geven nokh a kleyn yingl.

00:26:42.310 --> 00:26:46.890
eyner hot geheysn Yosef. der tsveyter hot geheysn Yankl, ha- ha-

00:26:44.824 --> 00:26:48.699
flegt ir mit zey tsunoyfkumen oyf a shabes oder oyf a yontev?

00:26:47.524 --> 00:26:50.676
yo. me fleg, yo, me fleg zayn

00:26:50.676 --> 00:26:52.446
azoy ibergegebn.

00:26:52.958 --> 00:26:55.584
eyner dem tsveytn flegt aroyshelfn

00:26:55.692 --> 00:26:58.149
az s'iz geven shlekht mit parnose

00:26:58.543 --> 00:26:59.831
flegt men

00:26:59.831 --> 00:27:01.119
aroyshelfn.

00:27:01.193 --> 00:27:03.313
 vos zol ikh zogn?

00:27:03.893 --> 00:27:06.396
az do in Amerike, in CANADA

00:27:06.396 --> 00:27:07.695
mishpokhe

00:27:07.695 --> 00:27:09.894
zenen a bisl dervaytert

00:27:10.018 --> 00:27:14.450
un dortn in Poyln UNK zenen gevezn mer frayntshaft, mer

00:27:15.283 --> 00:27:16.951
zey hobn, zey hobn azoy ⟨gevoynt⟩

00:27:16.951 --> 00:27:19.260
mayne brider, mayne shvester

00:27:19.333 --> 00:27:21.115
hobn a sakh ⟨getun⟩

00:27:22.118 --> 00:27:25.369
ven undz hobn gevoynt in Poyln, iz men gekumen fun Rusland

00:27:25.898 --> 00:27:28.249
hobn zey a sakh ⟨getun⟩. zey hobn undz

00:27:28.249 --> 00:27:29.486
ibergeshikt

00:27:29.627 --> 00:27:30.836
gelt

00:27:31.129 --> 00:27:33.840
⟨ibergeshipt⟩, ibergeshikt zakhn

00:27:34.437 --> 00:27:36.118
zey hobn afilek

00:27:36.158 --> 00:27:38.751
geshikt gelt az mir zoln konen

00:27:38.841 --> 00:27:40.162
batsoln

00:27:40.162 --> 00:27:42.423
far di shif, far di shif's kart

00:27:42.423 --> 00:27:45.618
me zol konen forn fun Poyln keyn CANADA

00:27:45.760 --> 00:27:47.593
hobn zey undz geshikt gelt.

00:27:47.920 --> 00:27:48.909
me shikt

00:27:49.033 --> 00:27:53.718
gelt in, in Poyln oyf yontoyvim ⟨OR⟩ peysekh oyf a yontev.

00:27:53.826 --> 00:27:55.119
s'iz geven

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:58.157
shtark ibergegebn. zey hobn

00:27:59.547 --> 00:28:03.051
 mayn shvester, mayn shvoger hobn m- alts ⟨getun⟩

00:28:03.276 --> 00:28:04.873
az me zol konen

00:28:05.014 --> 00:28:07.606
undz aribernemen fun Poyln

00:28:08.237 --> 00:28:09.648
keyn CANADA, yo.

00:28:10.482 --> 00:28:13.935
velkhe dervartungen hot ir gehat fun Kanade?

00:28:13.553 --> 00:28:14.323
?

00:28:14.278 --> 00:28:17.731
eyder, eyder ir zent geforn aher keyn Kanade

00:28:17.839 --> 00:28:20.516
velkhe dervartungen hot ir gehat?

00:28:21.366 --> 00:28:24.485
vos hot ir gemeynt? vos far a land vet Kanade zayn?

00:28:24.522 --> 00:28:25.646
oh

00:28:26.513 --> 00:28:27.767
vos vet zayn?

00:28:27.767 --> 00:28:29.780
ikh bin geforn a bisl

00:28:31.407 --> 00:28:32.649
nit ruik.

00:28:32.807 --> 00:28:35.872
kh'hob nisht gevust, az me kon nisht di shprakh

00:28:36.300 --> 00:28:39.129
 men kumt

00:28:39.861 --> 00:28:41.798
hob, kh'hob zikh a bisl

00:28:42.642 --> 00:28:43.939
geshrokn

00:28:45.126 --> 00:28:49.811
vi nor m'vet konen zikh do aynordenen, un vu nor m'vet konen krign arbet

00:28:50.020 --> 00:28:51.448
nor me

00:28:51.555 --> 00:28:55.194
di shvester, der shvoger, ⟨zey⟩ flegn ale mol shraybn

00:28:55.268 --> 00:28:57.506
"kum tsu forn,

00:28:57.850 --> 00:29:01.607
mir lebn gants gut, un vest oykhet lebn

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:03.209
mentshlekh, ve-

00:29:06.996 --> 00:29:10.410
nu, dos iz UNK efsher UNK
